.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, blood-red, yellow, chestnut
1. the person who likes yellow is between the person who likes blood-red and the person who likes blue##2
2. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Color   | chestnut | blood-red | yellow | blue |

